index.php?/profile/40700-kaspervld/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002240700\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/40700-kaspervld/\u0022 id=\u0022ips_uid_9986_3\u0022 rel=\u0022external\u0022\u003E@KasperVld\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0- the page button which looks like this\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u00221l75gyU.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/1l75gyU.png\u0022\u003Ewill allow users to add a horizontal line. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdded it to the large editor.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kiwi1960","CreatedById":81697,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-26T21:07:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222690988\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221469490413\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 hours ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat can I do to increase my chances of becoming a moderator, should the opportunity arise?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGrovel! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222691671\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221469541159\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHTML is cheating, though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome say having Mods in KSP is cheating... I therefore I suggest we all take your answer with a pinch of salt... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-26T21:13:33Z\u0022 title=\u002207/26/2016 09:13  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 26, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by kiwi1960\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-26T21:23:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222692246\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221469567257\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002281697\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kiwi1960\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, kiwi1960 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[...]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome say having Mods in KSP is cheating... I therefore I suggest we all take your answer with a pinch of salt... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s no such thing as cheating in a single-player forum...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry, just habit typing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maverick_aus","CreatedById":149050,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-27T08:01:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222691668\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221469541013\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny word about the borked IMGUR album problems? Is there a work-around? If there is a thread about this, just point me to the right direction... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi guys,\u003Cbr\u003E\nYep same question as adsii1970. Mods, what do we know about the imgur album button vanishing? And do we know yet if it will be back anytime soon?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-27T10:48:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222692910\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221469606479\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022149050\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Maverick_aus\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Maverick_aus said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi guys,\u003Cbr\u003E\nYep same question as adsii1970. Mods, what do we know about the imgur album button vanishing? And do we know yet if it will be back anytime soon?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s disabled until it gets fixed, no ETA at this time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/144601-imgur-album-embedding-looks-a-bit-broken/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;embedComment=2691800\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maverick_aus","CreatedById":149050,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-27T12:33:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222692995\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221469616490\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s disabled until it gets fixed, no ETA at this time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you for the reply and\u00A0update \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/12858-red-iron-crown/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002212858\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/12858-red-iron-crown/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Red Iron Crown\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kiwi1960","CreatedById":81697,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-27T21:18:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight..... I have a serious question for the moderators.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKeep in mind that I am 56 and no child or young teen that is titillated (is that word allowed?) with silly child sexual talk....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis forums is becoming a joke...... seriously...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen I talked about a B O O B Y prize.... the word was censored to \u0022Bloby\u0022 which isn\u0027t even a word... I corrected it twice only to have the same thing happen... I thought it was me with my double vision making the typos but then I twigged that it was the word censor. B O O B Y is a legitimate word... when talking about a B O O B Y prize, there is no alternative.... but that word is censored... it shouldn\u0027t be! I know this is a family site, but you would have to be.... strange.... to consider that word needed to be censored.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis site is fast becoming a joke... there are rules to tell us what we cannot talk about... words we cannot use.... and fair enough IN SOME CASES.... but NOT that word.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is a bird called the Red-footed b o o b y (Sula sula) ..... we cannot talk about that bird either!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy question is.... why does this site act like a nanny with such an overly strict word censor... there is no need for it surely.... some words... YES.... but dammit (is that word allowed?) its TOO STRICT!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever..... the word you are thinking of ends in an IE .... not a Y .... seriously.... its getting to be like a Kindergarten here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-27T21:20:22Z\u0022 title=\u002207/27/2016 09:20  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 27, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by kiwi1960\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}